    {
      "id": "sybil_19_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_19",
      "description": "Offering a driver-focused example with exceptional mechanical provenance. This unit features a high-revving naturally aspirated powerplant with optimized volumetric efficiency and a crisp-shifting short-throw manual gearbox. Recent maintenance includes a comprehensive refresh of the cooling system and a suspension overhaul utilizing polyurethane bushings and adjustable dampers for sharpened turn-in and reduced body roll. The limited-slip differential remains tight, ensuring linear power delivery through the apex. While the chassis shows minor cosmetic patina consistent with spirited use, the drivetrain remains robust with excellent compression across all cylinders and a recalibrated ECU for a broader torque curve. A true enthusiast's build ready for the track or technical backroads.",
